{"tid":11781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上海自由貿易區嚴禁資金非法流出!!!!!!!","createTime":"2016-11-29T11:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T13:18:16.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d01f8c78dd453cf6d59c6ae20d73234dc5fd74ee","tid":11781,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"自貿區的自由貿易帳戶監管進一步加強，想藉機大筆錢出境，沒門。 <br />\n<br />\n《自貿區郵報》報導，11月25日，央行上海總部召集轄內銀行開會，要求銀行加強對外省市資金流入上海自貿區的盡職調查，以及非法個人資金通過自由貿易賬戶（FT）對外投資，支持實體經濟，控制非法流出。一位參會的滬上某銀行國際部相關人士表示：「不能非法募集個人資金通過FT平台集合對外投資」;「總體要求就是促流入，控非法流出。」 <br />\n<br />\n那些讓境內的資金出境大筆購房的，大筆投資的，恐怕都已經進入了法眼。 <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_49818dcb0102x5js.html?tj=fina\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.sina.com.cn%2Fs%2Fblog_49818dcb0102x5js.html%3Ftj%3Dfina&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=dcdd235c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_49818dcb0102x5js.html?tj=fina</a>"},{"pid":"4b2a1e3b42c78c0c8de3d1b17504e7b790453614","tid":11781,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1d7201e799b7b4c9e78c103042b73da368d082","tid":11781,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"瞓左冇睇，上海超越左香港未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6acee6d4e44307926f52093a26427cec84cc7e","tid":11781,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec0c3dd58fad89ded53dee798eb3bcbfcf5d4d2","tid":11781,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自由貿易區"},{"pid":"2a40f7ba295767ec89b0b336e562d48fe1881227","tid":11781,"uid